      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is accompanied with &lt;a href=&#34;https://athletic.yudocaa.in/fitness/&#34;&gt;Hope&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is to maintain a daily journal of the efforts. This is to be seen from bottom&#xA;to top.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To explain the jargons:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;cw: current weight&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;gw: goal weight&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ok, lets start.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;march-24-2021&#34;&gt;March 24, 2021&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;cw: 73.9&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;A day of Freeletics. I really need to get my bicycle crunches right without&#xA;hurting my neck. The first set I did it as wrong as it could be. The later ones&#xA;were better. Hopefully it gets better. What I loved? Jump Squats.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
